# ─── OS + editor noise ─────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*~

# ─── Build output / dependencies (if you ever add a build step) ───
node_modules/
dist/
.cache/
.parcel-cache/
.netlify/

# ─── Reference-only folders that should never ship to production ──
# Pattern catches any future *_Loveable, *_Reference, *_Archive folder
# so you never have to think about this again.
*_Loveable/
*_Reference/
*_Archive/
*_archive/
*_refs/

# ─── Asset backups + intermediate work-in-progress files ──────────
# We keep originals out of the deploy. Drop them in /caboodle-site-archive/
# one folder up — already set up and gitignored by being outside the repo.
*.bak
*.bak.*
*.backup.*
*.original.*
*.orig.*
*_draft.*
*_wip.*

# ─── Big source files we don't want to accidentally commit ────────
# If you need 3D source models or raw video, keep them in the archive folder.
*.psd
*.ai
*.sketch
*.fig

# ─── Env + secrets ────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
